{
  "stem": "26790.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If I say something, I do it because I don't want to get killed by the bloody German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I want to be alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Please pay me the money which you owe me and tonight I finish and tomorrow morning I'm going to Russia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "From our town, Chelm, to the new Russian border, was only about 10 or 12 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "For me, for a young man to walk 10 or 12 kilometers is like nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyway, and he still keep talking, talking, [INAUDIBLE] me not to go, not to go, wouldn't help you nothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I am going, that's all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In the afternoon, I finish work, he pay me-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now let me speak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "How much?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this is a very interesting thing-- interesting thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Go on.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Go on.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will not say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What he pay me wasn't bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the [INAUDIBLE] month [INAUDIBLE] he pay me $0.10 a week, [INAUDIBLE] something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That type of money, this was money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after that, when I improving in my working, he pay me more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I want increase every couple months, something like that-- increase in the wages, that's all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, I got increases in my work, I got more-- more-- new-- the job to do it [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What Friday evening?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, Friday evening.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGH] That was not Friday evening, that was a-- that's a couple of days later because the Friday evening, that was the first day when the-- when the German start to cross the border and when they bombed Chelm.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was nothing, that was-- but what will be-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But after-- on Saturday, on Sunday-- we hear what the German is doing to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The hang him and shoot him, and they kill him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
